---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="月度深度 | 1H币研" description="每月比特币 & 以太坊深度技术分析，结合 Al Brooks 价格行为学与链上数据，提供中长期交易计划。" lang="zh" activeNav="monthly">
<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "月度深度",
  "description": "每月比特币 & 以太坊深度技术分析，结合 Al Brooks 价格行为学与链上数据，提供中长期交易计划。",
  "inLanguage": "zh-CN",
  "datePublished": "2026-01-31T20:00:00+08:00",
  "dateModified": new Date().toISOString(),
  "author": {
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "1H Crypto Trader"
  },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "1H币研",
    "logo": {
      "@type": "ImageObject",
      "url": "https://1hcrypto.com/favicon.svg"
    }
  },
  "mainEntityOfPage": {
    "@type": "@id",
    "@id": "https://1hcrypto.com/zh/monthly/"
  }
})}</script>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">月度深度</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] text-sm">每月最后一日发布 · 中长期结构分析 + 链上数据解读 + 下月操作计划</p>
    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-[var(--border)]">每月最后一日 20:00 更新</span>
      <span>|</span>
      <span>覆盖 BTC & ETH 月线结构</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 最新月度深度 -->
  <div class="mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <div class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">最新深度</h2>
      <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] ml-2">2026-05</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/20">BTC/USDT</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 border border-purple-500/20">ETH/USDT</span>
        <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">月度</span>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">BTC 月度深度：突破在即，准备迎接新高</h3>

      <!-- 月度关键数据 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-6">
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">本月开盘</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white">$68,500</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">本月收盘</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">$73,850</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">月线涨幅</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">+7.8%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3 text-center">
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">模拟盘 P&L</div>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">+$12,400</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 月度分析 -->
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-6 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-white">月线结构：</strong>5月月线收大阳，收盘价站稳 EMA20（$70,200）。月线连续两个月收阳，且 5 月低点 $68,300 高于 4 月低点 $65,800，Higher Low 结构确认。月线级别处于上升趋势中的健康回调后重启。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Al Brooks 月线信号：</strong>5 月 K 线为 Strong Bull Bar（收盘价接近高点，实体占比 > 80%），符合 Al Brooks 定义的「趋势延续形态」。上一根（4 月）为 Doji Bar，未能延续跌势，多头守住 $65,000 需求区，确认该位置为中期底部。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">链上数据：</strong>5 月交易所净流出 -48,200 BTC（数据来源：CryptoQuant），为 2026 年以来最大单月流出。长期持有者（LTH）地址余额增加 +32,100 BTC，筹码从交易所向冷钱包转移，卖压减轻信号明确。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">ETH/BTC 比率：</strong>5 月 ETH/BTC 从 0.045 升至 0.052，ETH 月度表现首次强于 BTC 自 2025 年 12 月以来。山寨季（Alt Season）预期升温，但需等待 BTC  dominance 跌破 50% 确认。</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">下月关键位：</strong>阻力 $78,000（月线前高）· $82,000（心理整数位）。支撑 $70,000（EMA20）/ $65,800（月线更高低点）。若 $70,000 失守，结构转为中性，需重新评估。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 下月操作计划 -->
      <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-4 mb-4">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">下月操作计划（6 月）</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▶</span>若回踩 $71,000–$72,000 且 1H 出现看涨 Engulfing Bar，做多，TP $76,000，SL $69,500</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▶</span>若突破 $75,000 且成交量放大，追多，TP $78,000，SL $73,000</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">▶</span>若跌破 $69,500 且 1H 出现看跌 Engulfing Bar，做空（短线），TP $67,000，SL $71,000</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mt-0.5">▶</span>仓位管理：单笔风险 ≤ 2%，总持仓 ≤ 10%</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 关联交易记录 -->
      <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-4 mb-4">
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2">本月关联交易记录</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <a href="/zh/trading/" class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-colors no-underline">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">多单</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white">BTC/USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">5/03 入场 · 5/28 止盈 →</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/zh/trading/" class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition-colors no-underline">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">多单</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-white">ETH/USDT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">5/10 入场 · 持仓中 →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/zh/daily/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-primary hover:underline">查看本月每日研判 →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 历史月度深度列表 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
      <div class="w-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--border)]"></div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">历史深度</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-04 月度深度</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC 月线 Doji · 震荡蓄力 · 模拟盘 +$3,200</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-03 月度深度</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC 突破 $70,000 · 月线大阳 · 模拟盘 +$15,800</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="card p-4 flex items-center justify-between hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors no-underline">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-1">2026-02 月度深度</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">BTC 回踩 $65,000 支撑 · Higher Low 确认 · 模拟盘 +$6,500</div>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 月度方法论说明 -->
  <div class="card p-6 bg-white/[0.02] border border-[var(--border)]">
    <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-3">月度深度方法论</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸</span>基于 Al Brooks 价格行为学，聚焦月线/周线结构</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸">整合链上数据（交易所净流出/流入、LTH 持仓变化）</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸">汇总全月模拟盘交易记录，P&L 透明展示</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">▸">下月操作计划：关键位 + 触发条件 + 风险管理</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
